                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Mileage: </span>25 kmpl</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Max Power:</span> 47.4 PS@7250 rpm</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Fuel Capacity:</span> 13.7 L</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Max Torque:</span> 52.3 Nm@5150 rpm</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="div-line"></div>
