                </div>
                <p> A recent addition to the lineup, the <span class="font-weight-700">Shotgun 650</span> brings a fresh aesthetic to the Royal Enfield stable. Built on the same 648cc twin-cylinder platform as the Interceptor and Continental GT, the Shotgun is styled as a <span class="font-weight-700">factory custom bobber</span>—low-slung, muscular, and incredibly stylish. </p>
                <p> Although still being introduced across markets, its expected Indian release in 2025 is already generating buzz. With a blend of <span class="font-weight-700">retro attitude and modern engineering, </span> the Shotgun is ideal for riders who want a unique machine with serious road presence. </p>
