                <p> The bike’s laid-back ergonomics, low seat height, and forward-set footpegs make it an easy-going mile muncher. It also includes <span class="font-weight-700"> Tripper Navigation </span>, a Bluetooth-enabled navigation pod that pairs with your smartphone. </p>
